version_description: Chords for "After the Zero Hour" by Wolf Alice.
First version, worked out by ear. This includes the synth line that plays throughout the song tabbed as a guitar part.
This tab uses very simple chords and requires a capo on the 1st fret.
This is based on the album version of this fantastic song.
Wolf alice - sadboy - No Capo - Link https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tF5DylpeQcw.
